NAME

  GBK - Source code filter to escape GBK script

SYNOPSIS

  use GBK;

DESCRIPTION

  The GBK software provides character oriented Perl scripting
  environment in GBK by easy installation and easy usage.

  - Character oriented regular expression
  - Byte oriented built-in functions
      and
  - Character oriented subroutines
  - Byte oriented regular expression on /b modifier

INSTALLATION

  Just copy GBK.pm and Egbk.pm to your @INC directory.
  for example, to C:\Perl\site\lib

SUBROUTINES

  GBK::length(charstring)
  GBK::substr(charstring, charpos, charlen)
  etc

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/

